{"id": "1301154687717736509", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "簡單來說\n用技能卡輸出的都怕遲緩\n詩篇鼠鼠和詩篇神父的差別如下\n詩篇鼠鼠\n優勢是 \n1.多段傷\n2.有麻打控場\n3.100延遲狂氣 不怕沒有牌\n缺點是\n太脆 只要遇到驅散 基本上就要死了（尤其是遇到米粒\n詩篇神父\n優勢是\n1.單體高傷驅散\n2.血量高\n缺點是\n害怕敵人有全體阻擋（可以靠隊友解決\n狂氣與技能卡不掛鉤 加上沒有成長性 基本上綁定潘的強效加成", "timestamp": "2024-10-30T12:04:11.837000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1301156279594782751", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "而且都很難爆發殺死對手", "timestamp": "2024-10-30T12:10:31.370000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1301156316043284530", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "這情況下脆皮鼠鼠就有點慘了", "timestamp": "2024-10-30T12:10:40.060000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1301156696798003220", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "比如說\n用艾 潘 打神父的話\n由於 神父身上通常都沒有阻擋/兩層阻擋 所以即使朵爾的驅散 用在敵方的嘲諷上\n只要有完整狀態的艾的三費指定攻擊卡+任意的傷害技能 基本上就能點掉", "timestamp": "2024-10-30T12:12:10.839000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-10-30T12:12:30.049000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1301156962389594185", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "但鼠鼠的話有麻 加上鼠鼠有詩篇的話通常都維持在三層阻擋 用艾的話 某程度上會比較難打", "timestamp": "2024-10-30T12:13:14.161000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-10-30T12:13:29.806000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1301157467350106145", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "author_bot": false, "content": "而高量傷害會使敵方的狂氣增加\n點不掉的話會令自己更危險", "timestamp": "2024-10-30T12:15:14.553000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1301156279594782751", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
